headline: New Jersey Custodian Sweeps the 2025 Cintas Custodian of the Year Contest
summary: CINCINNATI, May 06, 2025--Dan Davis, from Deerfield Elementary School, has been crowned the 2025 grand prize winner.

headline: 3 Profitable Stocks to Consider Right Now
summary: Companies with solid operating margins have a competitive edge, allowing them to reinvest for sustainable expansion. The best of these businesses balance profitability with reinvestment, setting themselves up for long-term success.
